@node Bugs "Known BUGS"
@{fg highlight}Known BUGS
----------@{fg text}

- For some unknown reason, after running the automation demo in the
  Test/Test module several times, MSE's requesters no longer appear.

- Parsing of the ModeID tooltype doesn't always work properly.  This
  appears to be a bug in the compiler not MSE.  I'm working on a
  solution.   (** I think this was a problem with a system patch I was
  using - I believe it may not be a bug after all)
@endnode
